Schindler Appoints Juergen Tinggren as Chief Executive Officer

-- B y   L e i g h   B a l d w i n
-- 
2011-09-28T05:05:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/schindler-appoints-juergen-tinggren-as-chief-executive-officer.html
Juergen Tinggren will take over as
chief executive officer of Schindler Holding AG on Oct. 1,
replacing Alfred Schindler, who remains chairman, the company
said today in an e-mailed statement.  Luc Bonnard will leave the executive committe in March 2012
and remain vice chairman, the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Leigh Baldwin at 
 lbaldwin3@bloomberg.net  